  "mainOuterHtml": "<main id=\"MainContent\" class=\"content-for-layout focus-none\" role=\"main\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n      <div id=\"shopify-section-template--27935319752870__article_nBjnMW\" class=\"shopify-section\"><style data-shopify=\"\">\n  .article_content__wrpr {\n    padding-top: calc(16px / 2);\n    padding-bottom: calc(16px / 2);\n  }\n  .article__hero-banner, .article__hero-banner img {\n    border-radius: 10px;\n  }\n  .section-template--27935319752870__article_nBjnMW-padding {\n    padding-top:  calc(16px / 2);\n    margin-left: 12px;\n    margin-right: 12px;\n    padding-bottom: calc(16px / 2);\n  }\n  @media screen and (min-width: 787px) {\n    .article_content__wrpr {\n      padding-top: 16px;\n      padding-bottom: 16px;\n    }\n    .section-template--27935319752870__article_nBjnMW-padding {\n      padding-top: 16px;\n      padding-bottom: 16px;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n\n<link href=\"//dynamic-preview.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/t/18/assets/main-article.css?v=172269203489927186851771645050\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"all\">\n\n<div class=\"main-article__wrpr section-template--27935319752870__article_nBjnMW-padding color-scheme-1\">\n  <div class=\"article__hero-banner narrow-width\">\n    \n      <img src=\"//dynamic-preview.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/articles/img_4.png?v=1770809247&amp;width=800\" alt=\"Radiance Redefined Skincare the Ellara Way\" srcset=\"//dynamic-preview.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/articles/img_4.png?v=1770809247&amp;width=352 352w, //dynamic-preview.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/articles/img_4.png?v=1770809247&amp;width=800 800w\" width=\"800\" height=\"958\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    \n  </div>\n  <div class=\"narrow-width\">\n    <div class=\"article_content__wrpr\">\n      \n        \n            \n            <span class=\"date\">07 Jan 2026</span>\n\n          \n      \n        \n            \n\n          \n      \n        \n            <span class=\"article_blog_title\">Blog</span>\n\n          \n      \n        \n            <div class=\"article__content\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;margin-top: 10px;\">\n              <h1 class=\"h3\">Radiance Redefined Skincare the Ellara Way</h1>\n            </div>\n\n          \n      \n        \n            <div class=\"article__content\">\n              <h2>Welcome to the Ellara Philosophy</h2>\n\n<p>At Ellara, we believe that true radiance comes from within—but a little help from nature's finest ingredients never hurts. Our approach to skincare is rooted in the perfect balance of science, nature, and self-care rituals that transform your daily routine into moments of pure indulgence.</p>\n\n<h2>The Science of Glow</h2>\n\n<p>Radiant skin isn't just about what you see on the surface. It's about nourishing your skin at every layer with ingredients that work in harmony with your body's natural processes. Our formulations combine cutting-edge dermatological research with time-tested botanical extracts to deliver visible results you can feel confident about.</p>\n\n<h2>Nature's Radiance Boosters</h2>\n\n<p>We've carefully selected ingredients that have been celebrated for centuries for their skin-transforming properties. From vitamin C-rich botanicals that brighten and even skin tone, to hydrating hyaluronic compounds that plump and smooth, every ingredient in our collection serves a purpose. We never compromise on quality, and we never include anything your skin doesn't need.</p>\n\n<h2>Your Daily Radiance Ritual</h2>\n\n<p>Beautiful skin is built through consistency and care. We recommend starting with a gentle cleanse to prepare your canvas, followed by targeted treatments that address your specific concerns, and finishing with protection and hydration. Remember, skincare is self-care—take these moments for yourself.</p>\n\n<h2>The Ellara Difference</h2>\n\n<p>What sets Ellara apart is our commitment to transparency, sustainability, and results. We believe you deserve to know exactly what you're putting on your skin and why. Every product is dermatologist-tested, cruelty-free, and formulated with both your skin and the planet in mind.</p>\n\n<p>Ready to redefine your radiance? Explore our collection and discover the Ellara way to glowing, healthy skin.</p>\n            </div>\n        \n      \n\n      <hr class=\"hr\">\n\n      <div class=\"article_page__social-icons align_ment--start\">\n        <button class=\"button article_page__social-share\" onclick=\"sharePage()\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 48 48\" width=\"144px\" height=\"144px\">\n            <path d=\"M 36.5 5 A 6.5 6.5 0 0 0 30.236328 13.207031 L 30.121094 13.263672 L 16.738281 19.953125 L 16.623047 20.009766 A 6.5 6.5 0 0 0 11.5 17.5 A 6.5 6.5 0 0 0 11.5 30.5 A 6.5 6.5 0 0 0 16.626953 27.990234 L 16.738281 28.046875 L 30.121094 34.736328 L 30.230469 34.791016 A 6.5 6.5 0 0 0 36.5 43 A 6.5 6.5 0 0 0 36.5 30 A 6.5 6.5 0 0 0 31.671875 32.158203 L 31.460938 32.052734 L 18.080078 25.363281 L 17.871094 25.259766 A 6.5 6.5 0 0 0 17.869141 22.742188 L 18.080078 22.636719 L 31.460938 15.947266 L 31.666016 15.84375 A 6.5 6.5 0 0 0 36.5 18 A 6.5 6.5 0 0 0 36.5 5 z\"></path>\n          </svg>\n          Share\n        </button>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n      <div class=\"article_comments_section color-scheme-3\">\n        <div class=\"page-width\">\n          \n            \n\n            <div class=\"article_comment_form\">\n              <form method=\"post\" action=\"/blogs/news/radiance-redefined-skincare-the-ellara-way/comments#comment_form\" id=\"comment_form\" accept-charset=\"UTF-8\" class=\"comment-form\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"form_type\" value=\"new_comment\" style=\"\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"utf8\" value=\"✓\" style=\"\">\n                <h3 class=\"h3\">Leave a comment</h3>\n\n                \n\n                <div class=\"author_email_text\">\n                  <input type=\"text\" name=\"comment[author]\" id=\"author\" value=\"\" placeholder=\"Full name *\" required=\"\" style=\"\">\n                     <label class=\"visually-hidden\" for=\"author\">Full name * *</label>\n\n                  <input type=\"email\" name=\"comment[email]\" id=\"email\" value=\"\" placeholder=\"Email *\" required=\"\" style=\"\">\n                     <label class=\"visually-hidden\" for=\"email\">Email * *</label>\n                    \n                </div>\n\n                <div>\n                  <textarea rows=\"10\" cols=\"100\" name=\"comment[body]\" id=\"body\" placeholder=\"Message...\" required=\"\" style=\"\"></textarea>\n                    <label class=\"visually-hidden\" for=\"body\">Message... *</label>\n                </div>\n\n                <input type=\"submit\" value=\"submit now\" class=\"button btn-prime\" style=\"\"></form>\n            </div>\n          \n        </div>\n      </div>\n    \n<script>\n  const sharePage = async () => {\n    try {\n      await navigator.share({\n        title: document.title,\n        text: 'Check out this page!',\n        url: window.location.href,\n      });\n      console.log('Page shared successfully');\n    } catch (err) {\n      console.error('Error sharing the page:', err);\n      // Fallback to traditional sharing method if API is not supported\n      fallbackShare();\n    }\n  };\n</script>\n\n</div>\n    </main>",
